399
00:28:29.566 --> 00:28:31.035
Mm-mm.

400
00:28:31.037 --> 00:28:32.237
[Olga] <i>See. you're
winding yourself up.</i>

401
00:28:32.239 --> 00:28:33.239
<i>Go get some rest.</i>

402
00:28:33.241 --> 00:28:34.876
