445
00:33:33.308 --> 00:33:36.381
Do you love me?

446
00:33:39.754 --> 00:33:42.092
No. no. no.

447
00:33:49.607 --> 00:33:50.607
[mermaid shrieks]

448
00:33:50.609 --> 00:33:52.177
